title: [1508521049] El Pirata Detapas: Coach Challenge - Gordon Ramsay
description:
El Pirata Detapas 'The Pirate' face their first challenge when they have to serve 30 of Gordon Ramsay's guests.

Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title.
